$$\begin{aligned}
\left(\frac{a+b+1}{a+b}\right)^{c}= & \left(1+\frac{1}{a+b}\right)^{c} \geqslant 1+\frac{c}{a+b}=\frac{a+b+c}{a+b} \Rightarrow \\
& \left(\frac{a+b+1}{a+b}\right)^{2 c} \geqslant \frac{(a+b+c)^{2}}{(a+b)^{2}}
\end{aligned}$$

Therefore,
$$\begin{aligned}
\sum \frac{(a+b)^{2 c-1}}{(a+b+1)^{2 c}}= & \sum \frac{1}{a+b}\left(\frac{a+b}{a+b+1}\right)^{2 c} \leqslant \\
& \sum \frac{1}{a+b} \cdot \frac{(a+b)^{2}}{(a+b+c)^{2}}= \\
& \sum \frac{a+b}{(a+b+c)^{2}}=\frac{2}{a+b+c}
\end{aligned}$$

The inequality is proved!

